{
  "stem": "6076.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They seeked, looked, people who wanted to work for the Germans, you know, to clean their cars, to do the cooking, or to-- to-- to clean their houses, whatever.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But this was when the ghetto was open.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was an open ghetto, which for the first six months, we-- six months, we could travel.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We could travel from city to city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "People, you know, they were occupied making black-market, you know, business.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And life-- we-- people needed-- you know, we needed food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We needed to survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But after six months--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not too much.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was very, very difficult, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After the ghetto was closed, no Jews could leave the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was forbidden to walk from-- we could only walk from 6:00 in the morning to 7:00 in the evening.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then it was forbidden to go out on the street.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But for us, you could not leave the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You have to stay between your vicinity.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, of course, you could go visit your friends, but everything in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Ghetto life was ups and downs, I will say.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Certain people who had merchandise, they made black market with the Poles.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Like, a Pole will sneak in, you know, from his territory to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he will bring in some food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And to bring in some food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The first law, after they-- after six months of the-- the Germans came in, they-- the committee.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The committee was everything in our city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The first thing was for the Jews to wear the armband.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The second law was for the Jews to cut off the beards.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No man should wear-- have a beard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The third law--",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
